Global General Purpose Lab Refrigerator Market Insights
General Purpose Lab Refrigerator Market size was valued at USD 1.5 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 2.4 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 7.5% from 2024 to 2030.

General Purpose Lab Refrigerator Market Overview
The global laboratory refrigerators and ovens market has demonstrated significant growth, with the general-purpose lab refrigerator segment playing a pivotal role. In 2023, the market size was valued at $1.44 billion, and it is projected to reach $1.53 billion in 2024, reflecting a compound annual growth rate (CAGR) of 5.9%. This upward trajectory is anticipated to continue, with expectations of reaching $1.96 billion by 2028, marking a CAGR of 6.4%. The general-purpose lab refrigerator segment is projected to record a 5.4% CAGR, reaching $492.3 million by the end of the analysis period. This growth is driven by the increasing demand for reliable storage solutions in research and development, particularly within the pharmaceutical and healthcare sectors.

